Connline Library
****************

Copyright (C) 2011-2013  Intel Corporation. All rights reserved.



Provides a simple API to request a network connectivity to the connection daemon
present on the system.


Features
========

Supported Backends:
	- ConnMan
	- Network Manager
	- Wicd

Supported Main Loops:
	- Glib
	- ECore (EFL)
	- libevent


Compiling
=========

./autogen.sh

./configure   (see ./configure --help for more information)

make


Installation
============

make install


Documentation
=============

A doxygen html documentation can be generated in doc directory:

cd doc
doxygen doxydoc.conf


Take a look on examples in test/ directory.

